SUMMARY:In-Person: Singing Practice for Mighty Marching Chorus for the No Kings March
DESCRIPTION:Join us on March 14th in the Kehilla Sanctuary for Singing Practice for Mighty Marching Chorus for the No Kings March in Oakland on March 28th. Doors open at 2:00 pm. This even is for anyone who wants to sing. Registration is required. If you already responded to Ellen Robinson’s previous email\, you still must register via this link.  If you do not register\, you will not be admitted. \nA link to the song sheets will be provided upon registration.  Please print it out and bring it with you (or download to your phone)\, along with hand held percussive instruments (if you have them).  Be ready to sing you heart out!
URL:https://kehillasynagogue.org/event/in-person-singing-practice-for-mighty-marching-chorus-for-the-no-kings-march/
END:VEVENT
