SUMMARY:MULTI-ACCESS: Shabbat Morning - Vaykira - and Baby Naming
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a celebratory Shabbat morning service led by Sharon Grodin and Hazzan Shulamit Wise Fairman\, exploring parashat Vayikra\, the first Torah portion in the book of Leviticus. This service will include a baby naming ceremony led by Rabbi Dev Noily for Rafiel Chêne Gryphon Pisterman (they/she) and parents Bruin Christopher Runyan and Morgen Pisterman Pilon.   \nJOIN HERE  \nKehilla requires masking at all in-person\, indoor events\, except youth B’mitzvah ceremonies (mask-optional b’mitzvah ceremonies will be noted as such in the event title). See the full Kehilla COVID-19 Safety Protocols here\, and see other accessibility information here. \nAll events at Kehilla are scent-free. Click here for information about what it means to be scent-free.
URL:https://kehillasynagogue.org/event/multi-access-shabbat-morning-39-5-48/
CATEGORIES:Feature on Home Page,Services
