SUMMARY:VIRTUAL: Face-to-Face – a Jewish/Palestinian Reparations Alliance
DESCRIPTION:VIRTUAL: Face-to-Face – a Jewish/Palestinian Reparations Alliance\nNOTE: Time Change to 11am start for Second Sundays (effective 07/17/2023) \nMeeting Days: Second Sundays every month\, 11am-12:30pm/Fourth Sundays every month\, 5-6:30pm \nLearn how Kehilla is engaged in Palestinian allyship with Palestinians in the Occupied Territories. Our regular Sunday meetings address the current work of the Committee and ideas for what is being planned for the upcoming year. If you are interested in learning more about this committee\, please contact Face-to-Face at facetoface@kehillasynagogue.org \nPlease see our page: FACE-TO-FACE: A JEWISH-PALESTINIAN REPARATIONS ALLIANCE
URL:https://kehillasynagogue.org/event/virtual-face-to-face-a-jewish-palestinian-reparations-alliance-12-2/2026-03-22/
