SUMMARY:VIRTUAL: White Folx Decentering Whiteness Affinity Group Meeting
DESCRIPTION:We invite anyone who identifies as white\, whether or not you’ve been to these meetings before! We work experientially on de-centering whiteness at Kehilla and in ourselves — so that Kehilla is more welcoming for people of color.\n\n \nEmail us for the Zoom link: wfdwhitenesscontact@kehillasynagogue.org. \nInfo at: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1R5AyZAuK4CLpvQU7mJwDjqDjpCzXNg5C/edit#heading=h.gjdgxs
URL:https://kehillasynagogue.org/event/virtual-white-folx-decentering-whiteness-affinity-group-meeting-23/
END:VEVENT
